    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Obfuscation</strong></i> is a first-person psychological horror game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119050/extras/e8a5fbd2d0911ccef1ccde7e37a7566b.webp?t=1764601170\" width=780 height=34 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In <i>Obfuscation</i>, you’ll explore a vast, eerie house that’s constantly trying to devour you. The house doesn’t stay still - it shifts and changes, with more and more unexplainable phenomena appearing the deeper you go toward the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119050/extras/83b667c9792ed37067a1be37ce726102.poster.avif?t=1764601170\" width=780 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119050/extras/83b667c9792ed37067a1be37ce726102.webm?t=1764601170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119050/extras/903195f491e9bfd52feebf7ed38d561f.webp?t=1764601170\" width=780 height=34 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment that lets you immerse in the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration-focused, with the house constantly shifting and changing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slow-burn horror experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple gameplay, no complex mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There won’t be any long story text to read.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 1-2 hours of playtime.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video 